8.10.20  9:30 pm    In reality, are we actually sardines in a can?

      no

8.10.20  9:29 pm   How does your mind work in this way?

      standard operating procedure. company policy

8.10.20  9:27 pm   what is the ideal environment for watching a bill wurtz video?

      on a screen at least 13 inches in diagonal, with a sound system that at least SOMEWHAT produces bass frequencies. so that includes most any in-ear / headphone device, or any speakers with a reasonable amount of size/depth. EXCLUDES built-in smartphone speakers, tablet speakers, laptop speakers, headphones you're not wearing, etc

8.10.20  9:25 pm   What's a song that you have made that you feel the most proud of?

      i would prefer to make a new one to be most proud of

8.10.20  9:24 pm   i outline but my characters never listen its like they have free will and they're writing the story themselves nothing has gone as planned

     that's fantastic

     how do i fix this or should i just not

     it sounds like things are going great, but if you think something is wrong with how it's turning out, see if you can describe the problem to me further and i will see if i can come up with some solutions

8.10.20  9:20 pm   roughly how much editing for 1 second of video

      1 cubic centimeter

      songwriting / song-selection

     not yet

     how's that going?

     i am assuming it will go similar to the way it went last time, which was pretty good even though it took a while and i was laughed at

8.10.20  8:48 pm   What on earth is the scramble section of this website?

      anagrams

8.10.20  8:41 pm   Do you plan on making a new video soon

     yes but that's not really the important part. the important part is that i will make many many more videos and songs after that

     (like at the end of the month)

     that is probably too soon considering at least 60% of my studio is entirely different than it was before. need to give myself enough time to not fall flat on my face, even though the amount of time i have given myself is still probably too short, but that's life i guess

      also what's your opinion on gerbils?

     i'm impressed

      let me perform some calculations

      the most ridiculous thing ever

      this is difficult to answer because 1 instrument can count as 2 instruments (i've seen proof) and 2 instruments can count as 1 instrument (seen proof of that too) so the whole system breaks right there

      no

      i have never been asked a question more than once

      which thing, nevermind, yes

      i'll try

      how many do you want

      best food. airlines have the best food, to distract you from how high up in the air you are

      i don't know. hopefully i will come up with a way

      no but i can see why you would think that

8.10.20  4:41 pm   Was the bad foot tap the bad thing you did?

      that was just 1 thing in a long line of many bad things

8.10.20  4:27 pm   Do you think the moon is just a reflection of the sun?

      no. it is the surface that produces the reflection you are talking about. but because it's not perfectly smooth/reflective, we still see all the moon's unique surface patterns
